git stash list                       To List the stashes
git stash apply                      It removes the topmost stash in the list and also it keeps the stash in list
git stash pop                        It removes the topmost stash in the list
git stash drop                       It deletes the topmost stash in the list

git log                                    Shows commit history of the current branch only
git log main                               Shows the commit history of the branch named main
git log --oneline main                     Shows the commit history of the branch named main in one line
git log --oneline -5                       Shows last 5 commits only in oneline format
git log --oneline main -5



git log --since=10days                     Shows all commits made in the entire repository within the last 10 days.
git log --since=3monthsago                 Shows all commits made in the entire repository since 3 months ago

git log --since=10days file_name           Shows commits affecting a specific file within the last 10 days
git log --since=3monthsago file_name       Shows commits affecting a specific file since 3 months ago
git log -L 10,20:file-name                 Shows history of changes to a specific range of lines


